This project creates a simple database for Customer and orders in django and using Django Restframework to create APIs to perform create, read, update and delete operation on the database.

The user of the database is authenticated using OpenID Connect

http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/get-customers/?customer_id=b5754a20-a458-4c92-b58f-8d398a2f0079
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/get-customers/

curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/add-customer/ -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"name": "day"}'

http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/get-orders/?order_id=4e3c08d0-0e2a-45d3-81b3-4746be376a99

http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/get-orders/?customer_id=b5754a20-a458-4c92-b58f-8d398a2f0079

http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/get-orders/

curl localhost:8000/api/delete-order/8a9c07a0-169e-4636-a4d0-2990b86a605bd  -X DELETE

curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/add-order/ -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"customer_id": "eb6dac37-ba91-46f0-a34b-ac32e0dbe535", "item": "phone", "amount": 1212}'

{"id":"b67900f7-dd8d-4059-95a5-5c6e8c282c7a","item":"phone","amount":"1212.00","created_at":"June 23, 2024, 06:02 AM","customer":{"id":"eb6dac37-ba91-46f0-a34b-ac32e0dbe535","name":"John Doe","phone_number":"+1234567890"}}

curl -X PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/update-order/b67900f7-dd8d-4059-95a5-5c6e8c282c7a -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"item": "Laptop", "amount": 500000}'

Returns
{"id":"b67900f7-dd8d-4059-95a5-5c6e8c282c7a","item":"Laptop","amount":"500000.00","created_at":"June 23, 2024, 06:02 AM","customer":{"id":"eb6dac37-ba91-46f0-a34b-ac32e0dbe535","name":"John Doe","phone_number":"+1234567890"}}
